<subSubSection id="32AD0DEA35B8437985CBF40775D9F663" pageId="6" pageNumber="17" type="remarks">
<paragraph id="1D634F78F525777C99489A5B60E176CA" pageId="6" pageNumber="17">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D6C18D756A4B89CA32AE070F25AA4F01" pageId="6" pageNumber="17">
The Euro-Siberian species 
<taxonomicName id="9310CC1595E3BF846FFD7E8846D82791" baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" baseAuthorityYear="1758" class="Gastropoda" family="Bithyniidae" genus="Bithynia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="6" pageNumber="17" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="tentaculata">
<emphasis id="322B16133C829BBE90F17E3041730AA6" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="17">Bithynia tentaculata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Linnaeus 1758) has often been mentioned from Iran, Turkey and Greece. However, this species could not be found in Greece (
<bibRefCitation id="DBAA6A2B258CDE37B7870CA36395FA59" author="Gloeer, P" journalOrPublisher="Journal of Conchology" pageId="19" pageNumber="30" pagination="249 - 257" refId="B27" refString="Gloeer, P, Pesic, V, 2010. The Planorbis species of the Balkans with the description of Planorbis vitojensis sp. n. (Gastropoda: Planorbidae). Journal of Conchology 40: 249 - 257" title="The Planorbis species of the Balkans with the description of Planorbis vitojensis sp. n. (Gastropoda: Planorbidae)." volume="40" year="2010">
<normalizedToken id="C91508788627A40A499813F466B10010" originalValue="Glöer">Gloeer</normalizedToken>
et al. 2010
</bibRefCitation>
) and probably does not occur in Turkey. The southern distribution border of this species lies possibly in N Bulgaria (Georgiev pers. comm.). An analysis of the specimens from NMB published by 
<bibRefCitation id="3540306AC01EC0EE97FBEFBB1E07C44A" author="Forcart, L" journalOrPublisher="Archiv fuer Naturgeschichte, N. F." pageId="19" pageNumber="30" pagination="404 - 447" refId="B19" refString="Forcart, L, 1935. Die Mollusken der nordpersischen Provinz Masenderan und ihre tiergeographische Bedeutung. Archiv fuer Naturgeschichte, N.F. 4 (3): 404 - 447" title="Die Mollusken der nordpersischen Provinz Masenderan und ihre tiergeographische Bedeutung." volume="4" year="1935">Forcart (1935)</bibRefCitation>
as 
<taxonomicName id="061FFA65B53874AE4BEB647E06F8E4A8" baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" baseAuthorityYear="1758" class="Gastropoda" family="Bithyniidae" genus="Bithynia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="6" pageNumber="17" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="tentaculata">
<emphasis id="F331AA4150029CEBF7D2E9705204C6AC" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="17">Bithynia tentaculata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
shows that these specimens represent 
<taxonomicName id="F61BC3DCC51653BF0A26AEBC23E863E0" authorityName="Glöer &amp; Pešić" authorityYear="2012" class="Gastropoda" family="Bithyniidae" genus="Bithynia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="6" pageNumber="17" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="forcarti">
<emphasis id="F1068188AA9F78AAF5B0B1D4535B9237" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="17">Bithynia forcarti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sp. n. (see below). Thus, 
<taxonomicName id="0DB88ED78FEF1838C483F0F1D0C41968" baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" baseAuthorityYear="1758" class="Gastropoda" family="Bithyniidae" genus="Bithynia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="6" pageNumber="17" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="tentaculata">
<emphasis id="3DB928B826D8F8D7F52C99F3673F903A" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="17">Bithynia tentaculata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
most probably does not occur in Iran and has been confused with 
<taxonomicName id="2B0936849196EFEB0FF480A09B4C268A" authorityName="Glöer &amp; Pešić" authorityYear="2012" class="Gastropoda" family="Bithyniidae" genus="Bithynia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="6" pageNumber="17" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="forcarti">
<emphasis id="C3FBB7100AB2DC72066A69AD1FEB2211" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="17">Bithynia forcarti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sp. n. or possibly with 
<taxonomicName id="553357EE5C73CFD4C67487B1C1161E1A" authorityName="Glöer &amp; Pešić" authorityYear="2012" class="Gastropoda" family="Bithyniidae" genus="Bithynia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="6" pageNumber="17" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="mazandaranensis">
<emphasis id="EBFEF889B1CA15852F459DE839217030" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="17">Bithynia mazandaranensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sp. n. (see below).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
